---
// About / Founder Section
// Per STRATEGY.md Section 4: "Led by makers, not managers"
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-32 px-6">
    <!-- Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
        <div
            class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-cyan-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <!-- Section Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold font-display mb-4">
                <span class="text-white">About </span>
                <span class="text-gradient">DigiDev</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-white/60 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Led by makers, not managers.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content Grid -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <!-- Left: Text Content -->
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-6">
                    <h3
                        class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-gradient-innovation flex items-center justify-center text-void"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                        The Venture Studio Model
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                        We're not a traditional agency. We build our own
                        products (REXZA, Taleem Space) and selectively partner
                        with visionaries who want to build the future of
                        Algeria.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-6">
                    <h3
                        class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-violet-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-violet-400"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                        AI-Native by Design
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                        Every product we build integrates AI from day one. Not
                        as a feature, but as the foundation. We leverage LLMs,
                        automation, and intelligent systems to create 10x better
                        experiences.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="glassmorphism rounded-2xl p-6">
                    <h3
                        class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-3 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-5 h-5"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                        Based in Algiers
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
                        Proudly building from Algeria for the world. We believe
                        in the untapped potential of North African tech talent
                        and are here to prove it.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: Stats / Visual -->
            <div class="glassmorphism-strong rounded-3xl p-8 text-center">
                <div class="mb-8">
                    <div
                        class="w-24 h-24 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-innovation flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/logo_symbol.png"
                            alt="DigiDev"
                            class="w-16 h-16"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold font-display text-white mb-2">
                        DigiDev Agency
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-white/50">Est. 2024 • Algiers, Algeria</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="py-4">
                        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gradient mb-1">
                            2+
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">Products Built</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="py-4">
                        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gradient mb-1">
                            AI
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">Native Stack</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="py-4">
                        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gradient mb-1">
                            48h
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">
                            Rapid Prototypes
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="py-4">
                        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gradient mb-1">
                            ∞
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-white/50 text-sm">Ambition</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
